        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[2024LPL 春季賽：UP 2-0 RA，UP 連下兩城完成驚天翻盤]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>2024 英雄聯盟 LPL 春季賽 UP vs RA，UP 2-0 RA，UP 連下兩城完成驚天翻盤。</p><p><img data-width="1178" data-height="723" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/B9/rBUBsmXfAEWAcyNjAAGiqYKPQ-E034.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><strong>第一局 BP</strong></p><p><img data-width="1352" data-height="746" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E2/rBUC6GXfAGaAR1GjAANHH3UklPM975.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><strong>賽況</strong></p><p>第 1 分鐘，RA 一級埋伏成功，naiyou 擊殺 H4cker 拿下一血。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E2/rBUC6GXfANuAXM2kAGk3aekSXJ4132.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 11 分鐘，RA 拿下小龍，後續團戰 UP 擊殺 naiyou。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E3/rBUC6GXfA5aAH4y-AKUvX-tQLHs906.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 22 分鐘，雙方河道團戰，UP 打出 1 換 3 隨後拿下小龍。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E3/rBUC6GXfA4uAH5IGALIc1ju5Yy0142.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 24 分鐘，RA 野輔陣亡，UP 拿下大龍。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E3/rBUC6GXfA6eAQYreAKpTjG7l4s8947.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 31 分鐘，UP 中路推進，Yuekai 收穫三殺，UP 一波 0 換 4 結束比賽。</p><p><strong>賽後數據</strong></p><p><img data-width="1298" data-height="709" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BA/rBUBsmXfA7qAQeE6AAJlEg1lAWI080.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1289" data-height="706" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BA/rBUBsmXfA8aAIwuzAAKWxLgZE5w554.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1288" data-height="698" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BB/rBUBsmXfA9yAMqdyAAJaVnTK_ho036.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><strong>第二局 BP</strong></p><p><img data-width="1356" data-height="755" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E5/rBUC6GXfCPSAFx9zAAQMh_ShjF0908.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><strong>賽況</strong></p><p>第 16 分鐘，雙方圍繞聽牌龍爆發團戰，Assum 拿下一血，RA 打出 1 換 3，UP 拿下聽牌龍，但 UP 中二塔被推。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E7/rBUC6GXfDYKAdVWVAMtOmYSYJ30413.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 21 分鐘，上路混戰，RA 打出 1 換 3 拿下大龍，UP 偷下電龍魂。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BF/rBUBsmXfDj2ABpx2AMvEiUCYYqY075.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 26 分鐘，賈克斯中路繞後 TP 配合大樹大招先手開團，Yuekai 背靠太陽圓盤換掉兩個，RA 打出 3 換 5。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BF/rBUBsmXfEA-ARgJUALn381NsH74710.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 27 分鐘，H4cker 搶下遠古龍擊殺 Xiaoxu 隨後再拿下大龍。</p><p>第 33 分鐘，遠古龍團，Assum 落單，UP 打出 1 換 3 拿下遠古龍。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BF/rBUBsmXfEAWAInCFAMj8V4v9HSc425.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 37 分鐘，UP 三龍匯推進，高地 1 換 4 一波推平基地。</p><p><strong>賽後數據</strong></p><p><img data-width="690" data-height="388" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/C0/rBUBsmXfENeAGqi-AAD5QxZXH48844.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="690" data-height="388" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E8/rBUC6GXfEN-AcPm4AAEcYKdu9Vg553.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="690" data-height="388" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/C0/rBUBsmXfEOSAfGTkAAEf4GWUk-M436.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>]]>
            </description>
